snippet.title: Celebrities Who DEFEND Amber Heard against Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
🖤 Celebrities Who DEFEND Amber Heard against Johnny Depp
We all know, Amber Heard and Johnny Depp’s explosive divorce continues to escalate, family, friends, and celebrities are throwing their support behind every star. Heard, who is 30 years old, was granted a temporary restraining order against her husband of 15 months, alleging in court documents that the actor, Johnny Depp, physically abused her throughout their 4-year relationship.
During this, Heard also claimed that Johnny Depp hit her with a cell phone, and most of all, he pulled her hair. She even submitted a photo of herself with what appears to be a bruise on her right eye as evidence against Johnny Depp.
